<h1 id="cc-title" class="text-center">Paladin</h1>

<h2 id="cc-subtitle" class="text-center mb-5">Oath of The Sacrifice</h2>

<p id="subclass-overview-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5 p-2 rounded"><i>The Oath of Sacrifice is an oath upheld by
    those who value the safety of their allies over their own. This oath is one of the most dangerous oaths a Paladin
    can take and those who choose to walk down this path understand the risk of doing so. However, being able to protect
    their friends, families and allies is well worth it.</i>
</p>

<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Tenets of Sacrifice</h1>

<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3"><b> No Price is Too High</b>: No matter what, you must be ready to be
  the shield. Your body is a small price to pay for the safety of others.</p>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3"><b>The Burden is Yours to Bear</b>: When the time comes, it is your
  responsibility to shoulder the pain of others and bring hope.</p>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3"><b>Know Who Deserves Your Shield</b>: While always ready to protect,
  know who deserves your sacrifice, as some will not appreciate it, and others will take advantage of it.</p>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5"><b>Live With No Regrets</b>: To be willing to put yourself in front of
  others, be proud of decisions you make and strive to leave behind a legacy worthy of your sacrifice.</p>

